title: Morningside Organic Bakery Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Take-out, Bakery
description: Funky organic bakery cafe and bookstore. Serves handcrafted sandwiches, salads, soups, noodles, smoothies, shakes, bread, pastries, raw food, chai, premium coffees and teas. Supports local organic farmers. Offer a unique collections of books to browse and buy. See website for upcoming films & events.
